# Student Exam Flow

- Student auth: **Admission Number + Exam Code** — no pre-registered roster for V1.
- Valid exam code maps to an active/open session.
- Pre-exam flow: Session Instructions → Exam Instructions → Begin Exam.
- Theory questions: never render text input — show booklet message with clipboard icon.
- Objective: A–D with immediate selection highlight (navy border/background).
- Flagged questions: amber in navigator.
- Submit: confirmation modal with unanswered count before final submit.
- Routes: `/student/login`, `/exam/[attemptId]`, `/exam/success`.
